{"id":3044,"date":"2021-07-31T00:09:53","date_gmt":"2021-07-30T17:09:53","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/thocaca.com\/?p=3044"},"modified":"2021-12-16T18:57:12","modified_gmt":"2021-12-16T11:57:12","slug":"ngu-van-11-nhung-nhan-dinh-hay-ve-cac-tac-pham-van-hoc","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/thocaca.com\/blog\/2021\/07\/31\/ngu-van-11-nhung-nhan-dinh-hay-ve-cac-tac-pham-van-hoc\/","title":{"rendered":"Ng\u1eef v\u0103n 11: Nh\u1eefng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh hay v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c t\u00e1c ph\u1ea9m v\u0103n h\u1ecdc"},"content":{"rendered":"\r\n<p>Xin ch\u00e0o c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n! C\u00e1c b\u1ea1n \u0111ang l\u1ea5y t\u00e0i li\u1ec7u mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed tr\u00ean trang web c\u1ee7a Th\u1ecf Ca Ca. \u0110\u1ec3 trang web ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n, nh\u1edd m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi chia s\u1ebb link web thocaca.com t\u1edbi b\u1ea1n b\u00e8, ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u00e2n gi\u00fap Th\u1ecf nha!<\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>Trong ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh Ng\u1eef V\u0103n THPT, m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 Ng\u1eef v\u0103n l\u1edbp 11 l\u00e0 hay nh\u1ea5t. \u00cdt t\u00e1c ph\u1ea9m th\u00f4i nh\u01b0ng t\u00e1c ph\u1ea9m n\u00e0o c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ed3ng ti\u1ec1n, b\u00e1t g\u1ea1o c\u1ea3. V\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u00f3 ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng t\u00e1c ph\u1ea9m n\u00e0y r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n trong k\u00ec thi t\u1ed1t nghi\u1ec7p THPT. C\u00f3 ai d\u00e1m ch\u1eafc &#8220;\u0110\u00e2y th\u00f4n V\u0129 d\u1ea1&#8221; kh\u00f4ng thi? Ai kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh &#8220;Hai \u0111\u1ee9a tr\u1ebb&#8221; s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eafc \u0111\u1ebfn. Sai l\u1ea7m nha!<\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>Nh\u1edb kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ea7m n\u0103m 2018, b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00e3 cho \u0111\u1ec1 b\u00e0i v\u1edbi d\u1ea1ng so s\u00e1nh. V\u00e0 2 t\u00e1c ph\u1ea9m c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i so s\u00e1nh l\u00e0 &#8220;Chi\u1ebfc thuy\u1ec1n ngo\u00e0i xa&#8221; v\u00e0 &#8220;Hai \u0111\u1ee9a tr\u1ebb&#8221;. Hai t\u00e1c ph\u1ea9m c\u0169ng khoai ph\u1ebft, n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng h\u1ecdc d\u1ea1ng so s\u00e1nh c\u00f2n m\u00f9 t\u1ecbt h\u01a1n \u1ea5y ch\u1ee9! Th\u1ebf n\u00ean kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ch\u1ee7 quan \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nha!<\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"wp-block-buttons aligncenter\">\r\n<div class=\"wp-block-button is-style-outline\"><a class=\"wp-block-button__link has-black-color has-vivid-green-cyan-background-color has-text-color has-background\" style=\"border-radius: 50px;\" href=\"https:\/\/drive.google.com\/drive\/folders\/1Le1FuZjqXNuTXbzXbCEE2i_AnNZ4xg8o?usp=sharing\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">T\u1ea2I V\u1ec0!<\/a><\/div>\r\n<\/div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>M\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec3 link \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y, cho b\u1ea1n n\u00e0o c\u1ea7n t\u00e0i li\u1ec7u n\u00e0y th\u00ec l\u1ea5y. N\u00f3 l\u00e0 g\u1ed3m c\u00e1c \u0111o\u1ea1n v\u0103n m\u1eabu, nh\u1eefng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh, nh\u1eefng n\u00e9t ngh\u1ec7 thu\u1eadt c\u00f3 li\u00ean quan,&#8230; M\u00ecnh l\u01b0\u1edbt qua th\u1ea5y b\u00e0i &#8220;S\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ecf&#8221; c\u1ee7a V\u0169 Tr\u1ecdng Ph\u1ee5ng c\u00f3 file t\u00ean l\u00e0: Ngh\u1ec7 thu\u1eadt tr\u00e0o ph\u00fang! C\u0169ng kh\u00e1 l\u00e0 hay \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1ee9???<br \/>Ch\u00fac c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n h\u1ecdc t\u1ed1t nh\u00e1!<\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<!-- AddThis Advanced Settings generic via filter on the_content --><!-- AddThis Share Buttons generic via filter on the_content -->","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<div class=\"mh-excerpt\"><p>Xin ch\u00e0o c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n! C\u00e1c b\u1ea1n \u0111ang l\u1ea5y t\u00e0i li\u1ec7u mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed tr\u00ean trang web c\u1ee7a Th\u1ecf Ca Ca. \u0110\u1ec3 trang web ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n, nh\u1edd <a class=\"mh-excerpt-more\" href=\"https:\/\/thocaca.com\/blog\/2021\/07\/31\/ngu-van-11-nhung-nhan-dinh-hay-ve-cac-tac-pham-van-hoc\/\" title=\"Ng\u1eef v\u0103n 11: Nh\u1eefng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh hay v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c t